---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro'

const lastUpdated = '2026-07-05'
---

<Page title="Now — Serina McFall" description="What's active right now, what comes next, what's still on the horizon.">
  <article class="now">
    <header class="opener">
      <h1>Now, next, and later.</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated <time datetime={lastUpdated}>{lastUpdated}</time></p>
    </header>

        <section>
      <h2>Now</h2>
      <p>vixenz.dev, this site, is my first Astro project and is in active build. Alongside it, Avalúne, my Next.js worldbuilding site, where I'm working on the canon reader and the database layer.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Next</h2>
      <p>Dev Academy AI Launchpad, 27 July through 13 November 2026 — 16 weeks of agentic coding on real codebases, with an industry placement at a NZ tech company. Deep on multi-agent workflows and production-code AI use.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Later</h2>
      <p>The Learning Companion Project, an AI-assisted study tool built on agent and worker patterns I'm currently learning. And the role this site is meant to find me.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Page>

<style>

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--lotus);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .opener h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: var(--text-lede);
    color: var(--mist);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .now section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .now h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--lantern);
  }

  .updated {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--mist);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

</style>